		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-dc957d5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="dc957d5" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-482807d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="482807d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Free open-source solvers, seamless integration, included in all AMPL licenses</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a901e07 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="a901e07" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>AMPL provides a selection of industry-leading open source solvers, enhanced with AMPL&#8217;s optimized interfaces for a seamless and efficient modeling experience. AMPL&#8217;s tailored solver integrations simplify model formulation, automate preprocessing, and unlock solver-specific performance features. </p>								</div>
