						<div class="elementor-icon-box-content">

									<h3 class="elementor-icon-box-title">
						<span  >
							Committed to Flexibility and Accessibility						</span>
					</h3>
				
									<p class="elementor-icon-box-description">
						At AMPL, we believe optimization should be accessible to everyone—from students and researchers to professionals and businesses. That’s why we offer seamless integration with leading open-source solvers, enhanced with AMPL’s solver interfaces for improved usability, automated reformulation, and streamlined workflows. With AMPL, you can leverage the power of open-source solvers without the typical complexities of setup and configuration, making it easier than ever to develop and test optimization models.					</p>
				
			</div>
			
		</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				</div>
