				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Enhanced solver interfaces</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f5912b2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="f5912b2" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Maximizing Solver Performance with AMPL MP</p>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-af95932 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="af95932" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>AMPL MP is more than just a solver integration tool &#8211; it&#8217;s as bridge that enhances solver performance and usability within AMPL. Unlike raw solver interfaces, AMPL MP provides a unified, solver-agnostic framework that allows users to maximize solver efficiency without manual model adjustments. With built-in features like automatic reformulation and advanced solver interactions, AMPL MP ensures seamless, high-performance optimization for a wide range of problem types. </p>								</div>
				</div>
