						<span  >
							Optimized Solver Integration						</span>
					</h3>
				
									<p class="elementor-icon-box-description">
						AMPL MP provides enhanced interfaces that refine how solvers interact with your models, ensuring greater efficiency and usability.					</p>
				
			</div>
			
