						<div class="elementor-icon-box-content">

									<h3 class="elementor-icon-box-title">
						<span  >
							Seamless Solver Compatibility						</span>
					</h3>
				
									<p class="elementor-icon-box-description">
						AMPL MP ensures that solvers built for AMPL are not just vendor solvers in their raw form. Instead, AMPL's solver interfaces provide additional optimizations, allowing you to achieve more without altering your models.					</p>
				
